Description:
Founded over 40 years ago, SAIL Outdoors Inc. is a Canadian company whose Head Office is located in Laval. SAIL Outdoors brings together professionals from all over the spectrum who share their talents and experiences to enhance “their” stores, situated in Québec and Ontario. SAIL stores offer the vastest selection of brand-name products within the largest outdoors, camping, hunting, and fishing network in Eastern Canada!
Job description:
As a Cashier, you are the first and the last person that comes into contact with our customers. You crown their in-store experience.
Day-to-day, you will work alongside your Department Manager. Your involvement includes:
Processing various transactions at the cash and ensuring accurate prices while doing so;
Promote the VIP program;
Wrapping merchandise for your clients;
Ensuring that your cash is balanced at the end of your shift and tracking problems if this is not the case.
The best moments of your story have made you someone who:
loves people and easily connects with others;
is sometimes teased by those close to you for your meticulous attention to detail;
adapts well into a routine but doesn’t mind when things move fast!
*** Salary: From $15.00 per hour
Tell us your best story!
